data.title: Lola Van Wagenen
data.meta_description: Lola Van Wagenen. Producer: The State of Marriage. Lola Van Wagenen was born on 19 December 1938 in Provo, Utah, USA. She is a producer, known for The State of Marriage (2015), American Experience (1987) and The Mike Douglas Show (1961). She has been married to George Burrill since 17 July 2002. She was previously married to Robert Redford.
